less thing to worry about. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eFor reference, back in \u003ca href=\"https://www.epicgames.com/site/en-US/news/filing-suit-against-google-and-samsung-for-illegally-colluding-to-block-competition-in-app-distribution-and-undermining-the-epic-v-google-jury-verdict\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSeptember 2024\u003c/a\u003e, Fortnite developer Epic Games sued Samsung for allegedly conspiring with Google in an effort to \u0026#34;block competition in app distribution.\u0026#34; The developer specifically criticized Samsung\u0026#39;s \u003ca href=\"https://shop-links.co/link/?exclusive=1\u0026amp;publisher_slug=androidpolice\u0026amp;article_name=Epic+drops+its+Samsung+lawsuit+just+in+time+for+Unpacked\u0026amp;article_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidpolice.com%2Fepic-drops-its-samsung-lawsuit-just-in-time-for-unpacked%2F\u0026amp;u1=UUapUeUpU1028915\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Flatin_en%2Fsupport%2Fmobile-devices%2Fprotect-your-galaxy-device-with-the-new-auto-blocker-feature%2F\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow sponsored\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAuto Block\u003c/a\u003e feature, which, since July 2024, has been enabled by default. It essentially blocks downloads from sources other than the Google Play Store or Samsung\u0026#39;s own Galaxy Store.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"e2d7-4e60-812a1f494d44\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t\n\t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-google-in-hot-water-new-sideloading-changes/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1081\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A close up on a prompt to install the Epic Games store via sideload on a Pixel 9 Pro.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/09/sideload-hero-epic-2024.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026#34;Our litigation alleges that Samsung’s recent implementation of the Auto Blocker feature was intentionally crafted in coordination with Google to preemptively undermine the U.S. District Court’s remedy following the jury’s verdict in Epic’s case against Google,\u0026#34; wrote Epic at the time. Now, the gaming giant seems to have reversed course.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eAs highlighted by Epic Games CEO \u003ca href=\"https://x.com/TimSweeneyEpic/status/1942259929865420855\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTim Sweeney\u003c/a\u003e in an X (Twitter) post, via \u003ca href=\"https://www.theverge.com/analysis/699541/epic-games-settle-samsung-auto-blocker-lawsuit\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eThe Verge\u003c/a\u003e, the video game and software developer and publisher has dropped its court case against Samsung.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"details-remain-unknown-for-now\"\u003e\n                        Details remain unknown for now\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n    \n    \n    \n\u003cp\u003eThe CEO didn\u0026#39;t share any details. All we know is that the two parties met for a \u0026#34;discussion\u0026#34; and reached a settlement. \u0026#34;We are grateful that Samsung will address Epic’s concerns,\u0026#34; wrote Sweeney, which might suggest a change in Auto Block\u0026#39;s default status. Alternatively, Samsung might whitelist Epic\u0026#39;s app store, allowing it to bypass Auto Blocker by default. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eIn a comment given to The Verge, Epic said that it has nothing more to share beyond the X post, so we\u0026#39;re not entirely sure what agreements were made. We\u0026#39;re expecting to learn more through a potential blog post from either or both of the parties involved. \u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"df97-4195-b4fbe6aaef97\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t\n\t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/epic-games-mobile-free-weekly-games-every-thursday/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/epic-games-could-dominate-mobile-games-like-steam-does-pc-but-will-it-take-the-leap.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/epic-games-could-dominate-mobile-games-like-steam-does-pc-but-will-it-take-the-leap.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-co